    dc:title "Redescription and taxonomic status of Paguristes praedator Glassell, 1937 and P. oxyophthalmus Holthuis, 1959 (Anomura: Paguroidea: Diogenidae), with an emendation to the diagnosis of the genus Areopaguristes Rahayu & McLaughlin, 2010" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234100>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234101>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234102> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234100>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Areopaguristes praedator nov. comb. (Glassell, 1937). A, male holotype (SL 3.5 mm), AMNH- 12232; B – E, G, male (SL 3.2 mm), EMU- 3701 B; F, female (SL 3.1 mm), EMU- 6967 B. A, shield and cephalic appendages, dorsal view; B, sternite XII (third pereopods), ventral view; C, left fourth pereopod, lateral view; D, first pleopod, internolateral view; E, left second pleopod, inner view; F, left first pleopod, inner view; G, sixth abdominal tergite, left uropod and telson, dorsal view. Scale bars: A = 1 mm, B – G = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234100/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234101>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Areopaguristes praedator nov. comb. (Glassell, 1937). Male (SL 3.2 mm), EMU- 3701 B. Left mouthparts, inner view. A, maxillule; B, maxilla; C, first maxilliped; D, second maxilliped; E, third maxilliped. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234101/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234102>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Areopaguristes praedator nov. comb. (Glassell, 1937). Male (SL, 3.2 mm), EMU- 3701 B. A, chela and carpus of rigth cheliped, dorsal view (setae omitted); B, right cheliped, mesial view (setae omitted); C, second right pereopod, mesial view; D, third right pereopod, lateral view. Scale bars = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234102/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

